div.div: How to Handle Date & Time with JavaScript - Stack Diary

This post covers how to work with dates and times in JavaScript, including getting the current year, date, time, and day of the week, setting and manipulating dates and times, calculating differences between date and time periods, and much more. By utilizing the built-in Date object and the core features of JavaScript, you can perform a wide range of date and time operations for building web applications, games, and other types of software that require accurate time-based processing.
